category: Editors
build-depends: cygport 
sdesc: "Toggle visibility of hidden Org mode element parts upon entering and leaving an element"
ldesc: "This package, inspired by org-fragtog, enables automatic visibility toggling depending on cursor position. Hidden element parts appear when the cursor enters an element and disappear when it leaves."
skip:

homepage: https://github.com/awth13/org-appear
